{"id":4195,"date":"2025-06-16T14:13:30","date_gmt":"2025-06-16T07:13:30","guid":{"rendered":"https:\/\/gsccos.vn\/?p=4195"},"modified":"2025-06-16T14:13:30","modified_gmt":"2025-06-16T07:13:30","slug":"chi-so-chong-nang-spf","status":"publish","type":"post","link":"https:\/\/gsccos.vn\/thong-tin-nganh\/chi-so-chong-nang-spf\/","title":{"rendered":"Ch\u1ec9 s\u1ed1 ch\u1ed1ng n\u1eafng SPF l\u00e0 g\u00ec? Gi\u1ea3i m\u00e3 nh\u1eefng con s\u1ed1 tr\u00ean tu\u00fdp kem ch\u1ed1ng n\u1eafng"},"content":{"rendered":"<p><i><span style=\"font-weight: 400\">Khi t\u00ecm hi\u1ec3u c\u00e1c s\u1ea3n ph\u1ea9m b\u1ea3o v\u1ec7 da kh\u1ecfi t\u00e1c \u0111\u1ed9ng t\u1eeb \u00e1nh m\u1eb7t tr\u1eddi, nhi\u1ec1u ng\u01b0\u1eddi v\u1eabn th\u1eafc m\u1eafc: <\/span><\/i><a href=\"https:\/\/gsccos.vn\/chi-so-chong-nang-spf\/\"><b><i>ch\u1ec9 s\u1ed1 ch\u1ed1ng n\u1eafng SPF l\u00e0 g\u00ec<\/i><\/b><\/a><i><span style=\"font-weight: 400\"> v\u00e0 n\u00f3 ph\u1ea3n \u00e1nh \u0111i\u1ec1u g\u00ec trong hi\u1ec7u qu\u1ea3 b\u1ea3o v\u1ec7 da? Trong b\u00e0i vi\u1ebft n\u00e0y, ch\u00fang ta s\u1ebd c\u00f9ng kh\u00e1m ph\u00e1 \u00fd ngh\u0129a th\u1eadt s\u1ef1 c\u1ee7a c\u00e1c con s\u1ed1 SPF v\u00e0 vai tr\u00f2 c\u1ee7a t\u1eebng lo\u1ea1i tia UV \u1ea3nh h\u01b0\u1edfng \u0111\u1ebfn l\u00e0n da nh\u01b0 th\u1ebf n\u00e0o.<\/span><\/i><\/p>\n\n<h2><span class=\"ez-toc-section\" id=\"chi-so-chong-nang-spf-la-gi-chia-khoa-danh-gia-kha-nang-chong-nang-cua-san-pham\"><\/span><b>Ch\u1ec9 s\u1ed1 ch\u1ed1ng n\u1eafng SPF l\u00e0 g\u00ec? Ch\u00eca kh\u00f3a \u0111\u00e1nh gi\u00e1 kh\u1ea3 n\u0103ng ch\u1ed1ng n\u1eafng c\u1ee7a s\u1ea3n ph\u1ea9m<\/b><span class=\"ez-toc-section-end\"><\/span><\/h2>\n<p><span style=\"font-weight: 400\">SPF l\u00e0 vi\u1ebft t\u1eaft c\u1ee7a \u201cSun Protection Factor\u201d, t\u1ea1m d\u1ecbch l\u00e0 <\/span><b>h\u1ec7 s\u1ed1 b\u1ea3o v\u1ec7 da tr\u01b0\u1edbc tia UVB<\/b><span style=\"font-weight: 400\"> &#8211; lo\u1ea1i b\u1ee9c x\u1ea1 c\u00f3 th\u1ec3 khi\u1ebfn da b\u1ecb \u0111\u1ecf r\u00e1t, ch\u00e1y n\u1eafng ho\u1eb7c t\u1ed5n th\u01b0\u01a1ng nghi\u00eam tr\u1ecdng n\u1ebfu ti\u1ebfp x\u00fac qu\u00e1 l\u00e2u. M\u1ed7i \u0111\u01a1n v\u1ecb SPF t\u01b0\u01a1ng \u1ee9ng v\u1edbi kho\u1ea3ng 10 ph\u00fat da \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c b\u1ea3o v\u1ec7 d\u01b0\u1edbi n\u1eafng. Nh\u01b0 v\u1eady, kem ch\u1ed1ng n\u1eafng SPF 30 s\u1ebd h\u1ed7 tr\u1ee3 che ch\u1eafn l\u00e0n da kho\u1ea3ng 300 ph\u00fat n\u1ebfu \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c s\u1eed d\u1ee5ng \u0111\u00fang c\u00e1ch.<\/span><\/p>\n<p><span style=\"font-weight: 400\">Tuy nhi\u00ean, con s\u1ed1 n\u00e0y ch\u1ec9 mang t\u00ednh l\u00fd thuy\u1ebft. T\u00f9y v\u00e0o th\u1eddi ti\u1ebft, l\u01b0\u1ee3ng m\u1ed3 h\u00f4i, m\u1ee9c \u0111\u1ed9 ti\u1ebfp x\u00fac v\u1edbi n\u01b0\u1edbc ho\u1eb7c vi\u1ec7c thoa l\u1ea1i s\u1ea3n ph\u1ea9m \u0111\u00fang gi\u1edd m\u00e0 hi\u1ec7u qu\u1ea3 c\u00f3 th\u1ec3 thay \u0111\u1ed5i.<\/span><\/p>\n<h2><span class=\"ez-toc-section\" id=\"bao-nhieu-spf-la-du\"><\/span><b>Bao nhi\u00eau SPF l\u00e0 \u0111\u1ee7?<\/b><span class=\"ez-toc-section-end\"><\/span><\/h2>\n<p><span style=\"font-weight: 400\">SPF c\u00e0ng cao kh\u00f4ng \u0111\u1ed3ng ngh\u0129a v\u1edbi vi\u1ec7c ch\u1ed1ng n\u1eafng &#8220;v\u00f4 h\u1ea1n&#8221;. D\u01b0\u1edbi \u0111\u00e2y l\u00e0 hi\u1ec7u su\u1ea5t trung b\u00ecnh m\u00e0 c\u00e1c m\u1ee9c SPF ph\u1ed5 bi\u1ebfn th\u01b0\u1eddng \u0111\u1ea1t \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c:<\/span><\/p>\n<figure id=\"attachment_4196\" aria-describedby=\"caption-attachment-4196\" style=\"width: 800px\" class=\"wp-caption aligncenter\"><img fetchpriority=\"high\" decoding=\"async\" class=\"size-full wp-image-4196\" src=\"https:\/\/gsccos.vn\/wp-content\/uploads\/2025\/06\/69-1.webp\" alt=\"Bao nhi\u00eau SPF l\u00e0 \u0111\u1ee7\" width=\"800\" height=\"450\" srcset=\"https:\/\/gsccos.vn\/wp-content\/uploads\/2025\/06\/69-1.webp 800w, https:\/\/gsccos.vn\/wp-content\/uploads\/2025\/06\/69-1-300x169.webp 300w, https:\/\/gsccos.vn\/wp-content\/uploads\/2025\/06\/69-1-768x432.webp 768w, https:\/\/gsccos.vn\/wp-content\/uploads\/2025\/06\/69-1-600x338.webp 600w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 800px) 100vw, 800px\" \/><figcaption id=\"caption-attachment-4196\" class=\"wp-caption-text\">Bao nhi\u00eau SPF l\u00e0 \u0111\u1ee7<\/figcaption><\/figure>\n<ul>\n<li style=\"font-weight: 400\"><b>SPF 15<\/b><span style=\"font-weight: 400\">: Ng\u0103n \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c kho\u1ea3ng 93% tia UVB.<\/span><\/li>\n<li style=\"font-weight: 400\"><b>SPF 30<\/b><span style=\"font-weight: 400\">: B\u1ea3o v\u1ec7 \u0111\u1ebfn 97% tia UVB.<\/span><\/li>\n<li style=\"font-weight: 400\"><b>SPF 50<\/b><span style=\"font-weight: 400\">: Hi\u1ec7u qu\u1ea3 l\u00ean t\u1edbi 98%.<\/span><\/li>\n<\/ul>\n<p><span style=\"font-weight: 400\">S\u1ef1 ch\u00eanh l\u1ec7ch n\u00e0y tuy nh\u1ecf nh\u01b0ng c\u00f3 th\u1ec3 mang \u00fd ngh\u0129a l\u1edbn v\u1edbi l\u00e0n da nh\u1ea1y c\u1ea3m ho\u1eb7c trong \u0111i\u1ec1u ki\u1ec7n th\u1eddi ti\u1ebft gay g\u1eaft.<\/span><\/p>\n<h2><span class=\"ez-toc-section\" id=\"tia-cuc-tim-%e2%80%93-ke-thu-vo-hinh-cua-lan-da\"><\/span><b>Tia c\u1ef1c t\u00edm \u2013 K\u1ebb th\u00f9 v\u00f4 h\u00ecnh c\u1ee7a l\u00e0n da<\/b><span class=\"ez-toc-section-end\"><\/span><\/h2>\n<p><span style=\"font-weight: 400\">Tia c\u1ef1c t\u00edm chia l\u00e0m 3 lo\u1ea1i tia UV ph\u1ed5 bi\u1ebfn, c\u00e1c n\u00e0ng c\u00f3 th\u1ec3 tham kh\u1ea3o k\u1ef9 h\u01a1n \u1edf ph\u1ea7n d\u01b0\u1edbi\u201d<\/span><\/p>\n<h3><span class=\"ez-toc-section\" id=\"uva-%e2%80%93-tia-xuyen-thau-sau-thuc-day-lao-hoa\"><\/span><b><i>UVA &#8211; Tia xuy\u00ean th\u1ea5u s\u00e2u, th\u00fac \u0111\u1ea9y l\u00e3o h\u00f3a<\/i><\/b><span class=\"ez-toc-section-end\"><\/span><\/h3>\n<p><span style=\"font-weight: 400\">Chi\u1ebfm ph\u1ea7n l\u1edbn trong tia c\u1ef1c t\u00edm, tia UVA c\u00f3 th\u1ec3 xuy\u00ean qua m\u00e2y, c\u1eeda k\u00ednh v\u00e0 th\u1eadm ch\u00ed c\u1ea3 qu\u1ea7n \u00e1o m\u1ecfng. B\u1ee9c x\u1ea1 n\u00e0y khi\u1ebfn da m\u1ea5t \u0111i \u0111\u1ed9 \u0111\u00e0n h\u1ed3i, h\u00ecnh th\u00e0nh n\u1ebfp nh\u0103n, \u0111\u1ed1m n\u00e2u v\u00e0 c\u00e1c d\u1ea5u hi\u1ec7u l\u00e3o h\u00f3a s\u1edbm.<\/span><\/p>\n<h3><span class=\"ez-toc-section\" id=\"uvb-%e2%80%93-nguy-co-gay-bong-da-va-ton-thuong-te-bao\"><\/span><b><i>UVB \u2013 Nguy c\u01a1 g\u00e2y b\u1ecfng da v\u00e0 t\u1ed5n th\u01b0\u01a1ng t\u1ebf b\u00e0o<\/i><\/b><span class=\"ez-toc-section-end\"><\/span><\/h3>\n<p><span style=\"font-weight: 400\">Tuy ch\u1ec9 chi\u1ebfm kho\u1ea3ng 5% tia UV nh\u01b0ng UVB l\u1ea1i l\u00e0 nguy\u00ean nh\u00e2n ch\u00ednh g\u00e2y ch\u00e1y n\u1eafng. N\u1ebfu ti\u1ebfp x\u00fac l\u00e2u d\u00e0i, tia n\u00e0y c\u00f2n c\u00f3 th\u1ec3 ph\u00e1 h\u1ee7y ADN trong t\u1ebf b\u00e0o da v\u00e0 l\u00e0m t\u0103ng nguy c\u01a1 ung th\u01b0 da.<\/span><\/p>\n<figure id=\"attachment_4198\" aria-describedby=\"caption-attachment-4198\" style=\"width: 800px\" class=\"wp-caption aligncenter\"><img decoding=\"async\" class=\"size-full wp-image-4198\" src=\"https:\/\/gsccos.vn\/wp-content\/uploads\/2025\/06\/69-3.webp\" alt=\"UVB \u2013 Nguy c\u01a1 g\u00e2y b\u1ecfng da v\u00e0 t\u1ed5n th\u01b0\u01a1ng t\u1ebf b\u00e0o\" width=\"800\" height=\"450\" srcset=\"https:\/\/gsccos.vn\/wp-content\/uploads\/2025\/06\/69-3.webp 800w, https:\/\/gsccos.vn\/wp-content\/uploads\/2025\/06\/69-3-300x169.webp 300w, https:\/\/gsccos.vn\/wp-content\/uploads\/2025\/06\/69-3-768x432.webp 768w, https:\/\/gsccos.vn\/wp-content\/uploads\/2025\/06\/69-3-600x338.webp 600w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 800px) 100vw, 800px\" \/><figcaption id=\"caption-attachment-4198\" class=\"wp-caption-text\">UVB \u2013 Nguy c\u01a1 g\u00e2y b\u1ecfng da v\u00e0 t\u1ed5n th\u01b0\u01a1ng t\u1ebf b\u00e0o<\/figcaption><\/figure>\n<h3><span class=\"ez-toc-section\" id=\"uvc-%e2%80%93-loai-buc-xa-nguy-hiem-da-bi-chan-tu-khi-quyen\"><\/span><b><i>UVC &#8211; Lo\u1ea1i b\u1ee9c x\u1ea1 nguy hi\u1ec3m \u0111\u00e3 b\u1ecb ch\u1eafn t\u1eeb kh\u00ed quy\u1ec3n<\/i><\/b><span class=\"ez-toc-section-end\"><\/span><\/h3>\n<p><span style=\"font-weight: 400\">V\u1edbi b\u01b0\u1edbc s\u00f3ng ng\u1eafn v\u00e0 n\u0103ng l\u01b0\u1ee3ng cao, tia UVC c\u1ef1c k\u1ef3 nguy hi\u1ec3m. May m\u1eafn thay, t\u1ea7ng ozone \u0111\u00e3 h\u1ea5p th\u1ee5 g\u1ea7n nh\u01b0 to\u00e0n b\u1ed9 n\u00ean ch\u00fang hi\u1ebfm khi ti\u1ebfp x\u00fac v\u1edbi con ng\u01b0\u1eddi.<\/span><\/p>\n<h2><span class=\"ez-toc-section\" id=\"so-sanh-cac-muc-spf-30-50-va-80-co-gi-khac-biet\"><\/span><strong>So s\u00e1nh c\u00e1c m\u1ee9c SPF: 30, 50 v\u00e0 80 c\u00f3 g\u00ec kh\u00e1c bi\u1ec7t?<\/strong><span class=\"ez-toc-section-end\"><\/span><\/h2>\n<ul>\n<li style=\"font-weight: 400\"><span style=\"font-weight: 400\">SPF 30: L\u00fd t\u01b0\u1edfng cho ng\u01b0\u1eddi c\u00f3 l\u00e0n da kho\u1ebb, sinh ho\u1ea1t trong m\u00f4i tr\u01b0\u1eddng \u00edt ti\u1ebfp x\u00fac v\u1edbi \u00e1nh n\u1eafng.<\/span><\/li>\n<li style=\"font-weight: 400\"><span style=\"font-weight: 400\">SPF 50: L\u1ef1a ch\u1ecdn ph\u00f9 h\u1ee3p cho ho\u1ea1t \u0111\u1ed9ng ngo\u00e0i tr\u1eddi \u1edf c\u01b0\u1eddng \u0111\u1ed9 trung b\u00ecnh nh\u01b0 \u0111i l\u00e0m, \u0111i ch\u01a1i.<\/span><\/li>\n<li style=\"font-weight: 400\"><span style=\"font-weight: 400\">SPF 80: Ph\u00f9 h\u1ee3p cho nh\u1eefng m\u00f4i tr\u01b0\u1eddng n\u1eafng g\u1eaft nh\u01b0 leo n\u00fai, \u0111i bi\u1ec3n, l\u00e0m vi\u1ec7c ngo\u00e0i tr\u1eddi trong th\u1eddi gian d\u00e0i ho\u1eb7c da r\u1ea5t d\u1ec5 b\u1eaft n\u1eafng.<\/span><\/li>\n<\/ul>\n<p><span style=\"font-weight: 400\">D\u00f9 l\u1ef1a ch\u1ecdn m\u1ee9c SPF n\u00e0o, vi\u1ec7c thoa \u0111\u1ee7 l\u01b0\u1ee3ng v\u00e0 b\u00f4i l\u1ea1i \u0111\u1ec1u \u0111\u1eb7n sau m\u1ed7i 2 &#8211; 3 gi\u1edd v\u1eabn l\u00e0 \u0111i\u1ec1u ki\u1ec7n ti\u00ean quy\u1ebft \u0111\u1ec3 \u0111\u1ea1t \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c hi\u1ec7u qu\u1ea3 t\u1ed1i \u01b0u.<\/span><\/p>\n<h2><span class=\"ez-toc-section\" id=\"gsc-triple-sun-block-%e2%80%93-kem-chong-nang-vat-ly-lanh-tinh-bao-ve-toan-dien-cho-lan-da\"><\/span><b>GSC Triple Sun Block &#8211; Kem ch\u1ed1ng n\u1eafng v\u1eadt l\u00fd l\u00e0nh t\u00ednh, b\u1ea3o v\u1ec7 to\u00e0n di\u1ec7n cho l\u00e0n da<\/b><span class=\"ez-toc-section-end\"><\/span><\/h2>\n<p><span style=\"font-weight: 400\">N\u1ebfu b\u1ea1n \u0111ang t\u00ecm ki\u1ebfm m\u1ed9t s\u1ea3n ph\u1ea9m ch\u1ed1ng n\u1eafng d\u1ecbu nh\u1eb9, an to\u00e0n cho da nh\u1ea1y c\u1ea3m nh\u01b0ng v\u1eabn \u0111\u1ea3m b\u1ea3o hi\u1ec7u qu\u1ea3 cao, GSC Triple Sun Block ch\u00ednh l\u00e0 l\u1ef1a ch\u1ecdn \u0111\u00e1ng c\u00e2n nh\u1eafc. \u0110\u00e2y l\u00e0 d\u00f2ng kem ch\u1ed1ng n\u1eafng v\u1eadt l\u00fd \u1ee9ng d\u1ee5ng c\u00f4ng ngh\u1ec7 l\u1ecdc tia UV th\u1ebf h\u1ec7 m\u1edbi, k\u1ebft h\u1ee3p c\u00f9ng d\u01b0\u1ee1ng ch\u1ea5t t\u1eeb thi\u00ean nhi\u00ean, gi\u00fap da \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c che ch\u1eafn t\u1ed1i \u01b0u m\u00e0 v\u1eabn th\u00f4ng tho\u00e1ng su\u1ed1t ng\u00e0y d\u00e0i.\u00a0<\/span><\/p>\n<h3><span class=\"ez-toc-section\" id=\"ket-cau-nhe-tenh-%e2%80%93-khong-nhon-rit-khong-de-lai-vet-trang\"><\/span><b><i>K\u1ebft c\u1ea5u nh\u1eb9 t\u00eanh &#8211; Kh\u00f4ng nh\u1eddn r\u00edt, kh\u00f4ng \u0111\u1ec3 l\u1ea1i v\u1ec7t tr\u1eafng<\/i><\/b><span class=\"ez-toc-section-end\"><\/span><\/h3>\n<p><span style=\"font-weight: 400\">Kem c\u00f3 texture m\u1ec1m m\u01b0\u1ee3t, d\u1ec5 t\u00e1n v\u00e0 th\u1ea5m nhanh, kh\u00f4ng g\u00e2y n\u1eb7ng m\u1eb7t hay b\u00edt t\u1eafc l\u1ed7 ch\u00e2n l\u00f4ng. D\u00f9 b\u1ea1n c\u00f3 da d\u1ea7u hay h\u1ed7n h\u1ee3p thi\u00ean d\u1ea7u, s\u1ea3n ph\u1ea9m v\u1eabn mang l\u1ea1i c\u1ea3m gi\u00e1c kh\u00f4 tho\u00e1ng, m\u1ecbn m\u00e0ng, ph\u00f9 h\u1ee3p cho c\u1ea3 b\u01b0\u1edbc cu\u1ed1i c\u00f9ng trong chu tr\u00ecnh skincare l\u1eabn tr\u01b0\u1edbc khi trang \u0111i\u1ec3m.<\/span><\/p>\n<figure id=\"attachment_4201\" aria-describedby=\"caption-attachment-4201\" style=\"width: 800px\" class=\"wp-caption aligncenter\"><img decoding=\"async\" class=\"size-full wp-image-4201\" src=\"https:\/\/gsccos.vn\/wp-content\/uploads\/2025\/06\/69-5-1.webp\" alt=\"GSC Triple Sun Block\" width=\"800\" height=\"450\" srcset=\"https:\/\/gsccos.vn\/wp-content\/uploads\/2025\/06\/69-5-1.webp 800w, https:\/\/gsccos.vn\/wp-content\/uploads\/2025\/06\/69-5-1-300x169.webp 300w, https:\/\/gsccos.vn\/wp-content\/uploads\/2025\/06\/69-5-1-768x432.webp 768w, https:\/\/gsccos.vn\/wp-content\/uploads\/2025\/06\/69-5-1-600x338.webp 600w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 800px) 100vw, 800px\" \/><figcaption id=\"caption-attachment-4201\" class=\"wp-caption-text\">GSC Triple Sun Block<\/figcaption><\/figure>\n<h3><span class=\"ez-toc-section\" id=\"gsc-triple-sun-block-phu-hop-voi-ai\"><\/span><b><i>GSC Triple Sun Block ph\u00f9 h\u1ee3p v\u1edbi ai?<\/i><\/b><span class=\"ez-toc-section-end\"><\/span><\/h3>\n<ul>\n<li style=\"font-weight: 400\"><span style=\"font-weight: 400\">Ng\u01b0\u1eddi c\u00f3 l\u00e0n da nh\u1ea1y c\u1ea3m, d\u1ec5 k\u00edch \u1ee9ng.<\/span><\/li>\n<li style=\"font-weight: 400\"><span style=\"font-weight: 400\">Nh\u1eefng ai \u0111ang trong qu\u00e1 tr\u00ecnh \u0111i\u1ec1u tr\u1ecb da b\u1eb1ng retinol, acid, laser&#8230;<\/span><\/li>\n<li style=\"font-weight: 400\"><span style=\"font-weight: 400\">Ng\u01b0\u1eddi th\u01b0\u1eddng xuy\u00ean l\u00e0m vi\u1ec7c tr\u01b0\u1edbc m\u00e1y t\u00ednh ho\u1eb7c ti\u1ebfp x\u00fac \u00e1nh n\u1eafng l\u00e2u.<\/span><\/li>\n<li style=\"font-weight: 400\"><span style=\"font-weight: 400\">Ng\u01b0\u1eddi y\u00eau th\u00edch s\u1ea3n ph\u1ea9m ch\u1ed1ng n\u1eafng kh\u00f4ng h\u00f3a ch\u1ea5t, th\u00e2n thi\u1ec7n v\u1edbi m\u00f4i tr\u01b0\u1eddng.<\/span><\/li>\n<\/ul>\n<h2><span class=\"ez-toc-section\" id=\"ket-luan\"><\/span><b>K\u1ebft lu\u1eadn<\/b><span class=\"ez-toc-section-end\"><\/span><\/h2>\n<p><span style=\"font-weight: 400\">Gi\u1edd \u0111\u00e2y, b\u1ea1n \u0111\u00e3 hi\u1ec3u r\u00f5 h\u01a1n v\u1ec1 ch\u1ec9 s\u1ed1 ch\u1ed1ng n\u1eafng SPF l\u00e0 g\u00ec v\u00e0 c\u00e1ch c\u00e1c con s\u1ed1 n\u00e0y \u1ea3nh h\u01b0\u1edfng \u0111\u1ebfn hi\u1ec7u qu\u1ea3 ch\u1ed1ng tia c\u1ef1c t\u00edm. Thay v\u00ec ch\u1ec9 nh\u00ecn v\u00e0o SPF cao, b\u1ea1n h\u00e3y c\u00e2n nh\u1eafc \u0111\u1ebfn nhu c\u1ea7u, \u0111i\u1ec1u ki\u1ec7n s\u1ed1ng v\u00e0 \u0111\u1eb7c \u0111i\u1ec3m l\u00e0n da \u0111\u1ec3 l\u1ef1a ch\u1ecdn s\u1ea3n ph\u1ea9m ph\u00f9 h\u1ee3p nh\u1ea5t. V\u1edbi s\u1ef1 hi\u1ec3u bi\u1ebft \u0111\u00fang \u0111\u1eafn v\u1ec1 <\/span><b>ch\u1ec9 s\u1ed1 ch\u1ed1ng n\u1eafng SPF l\u00e0 g\u00ec<\/b><span style=\"font-weight: 400\">. B\u1ea1n ho\u00e0n to\u00e0n c\u00f3 th\u1ec3 ch\u1ee7 \u0111\u1ed9ng b\u1ea3o v\u1ec7 l\u00e0n da m\u1ed7i ng\u00e0y, d\u00f9 l\u00e0 tr\u1eddi n\u1eafng g\u1eaft hay khi \u0111ang ng\u1ed3i trong v\u0103n ph\u00f2ng.<\/span><\/p>\n","protected":false},"excerpt":{"rendered":"<p>Trong b\u00e0i vi\u1ebft n\u00e0y, ch\u00fang ta s\u1ebd c\u00f9ng kh\u00e1m ph\u00e1 \u00fd ngh\u0129a th\u1eadt s\u1ef1 c\u1ee7a c\u00e1c con s\u1ed1 SPF v\u00e0 vai tr\u00f2 c\u1ee7a t\u1eebng lo\u1ea1i tia UV \u1ea3nh h\u01b0\u1edfng \u0111\u1ebfn l\u00e0n da nh\u01b0 th\u1ebf n\u00e0o.<\/p>\n","protected":false},"author":7,"featured_media":4202,"comment_status":"open","ping_status":"open","sticky":false,"template":"","format":"standard","meta":{"_acf_changed":false,"footnotes":""},"categories":[16],"tags":[],"class_list":["post-4195","post","type-post","status-publish","format-standard","has-post-thumbnail","hentry","category-thong-tin-nganh"],"acf":[],"_links":{"self":[{"href":"https:\/\/gsccos.vn\/wp-json\/wp\/v2\/posts\/4195","targetHints":{"allow":["GET"]}}],"collection":[{"href":"https:\/\/gsccos.vn\/wp-json\/wp\/v2\/posts"}],"about":[{"href":"https:\/\/gsccos.vn\/wp-json\/wp\/v2\/types\/post"}],"author":[{"embeddable":true,"href":"https:\/\/gsccos.vn\/wp-json\/wp\/v2\/users\/7"}],"replies":[{"embeddable":true,"href":"https:\/\/gsccos.vn\/wp-json\/wp\/v2\/comments?post=4195"}],"version-history":[{"count":1,"href":"https:\/\/gsccos.vn\/wp-json\/wp\/v2\/posts\/4195\/revisions"}],"predecessor-version":[{"id":4203,"href":"https:\/\/gsccos.vn\/wp-json\/wp\/v2\/posts\/4195\/revisions\/4203"}],"wp:featuredmedia":[{"embeddable":true,"href":"https:\/\/gsccos.vn\/wp-json\/wp\/v2\/media\/4202"}],"wp:attachment":[{"href":"https:\/\/gsccos.vn\/wp-json\/wp\/v2\/media?parent=4195"}],"wp:term":[{"taxonomy":"category","embeddable":true,"href":"https:\/\/gsccos.vn\/wp-json\/wp\/v2\/categories?post=4195"},{"taxonomy":"post_tag","embeddable":true,"href":"https:\/\/gsccos.vn\/wp-json\/wp\/v2\/tags?post=4195"}],"curies":[{"name":"wp","href":"https:\/\/api.w.org\/{rel}","templated":true}]}}